@startuml sd_ExcelService_importVariableData
skinparam backgroundColor #F9FAFB
title ExcelService.importVariableData(file) - Excel可变数据导入

actor "调用方" as Client
participant "PayrollController" as Ctrl
participant "ExcelService" as ExcelSvc
participant "SalaryItemRepository" as ItemRepo
participant "Workbook\n(XSSFWorkbook)" as Wb
participant "Sheet" as Sheet
participant "Row" as Row

Client -> Ctrl: POST /api/payroll/import\nMultipartFile (Excel)
Ctrl -> ExcelSvc: importVariableData(file)
note right of ExcelSvc #F0F8FF
  **导入流程:**
  1. 读取文件流
  2. 创建XSSFWorkbook
  3. 解析Sheet[0]
end note
ExcelSvc -> ItemRepo: findByActiveTrueOrderBySortOrder()
ItemRepo --> ExcelSvc: List<SalaryItem>
ExcelSvc -> ExcelSvc: filter(无公式项) → variableItems
ExcelSvc -> Wb: new XSSFWorkbook(file.getInputStream())
ExcelSvc -> Wb: getSheetAt(0)
Wb --> ExcelSvc: Sheet
note right of ExcelSvc #F0F8FF
  **解析表头(行0):**
  B1=考勤扣款→colItemMap: 1→item.id
  C1=绩效工资→colItemMap: 2→item.id
end note
ExcelSvc -> Sheet: getRow(0)
Sheet --> ExcelSvc: headerRow
loop 每个数据行(r=1起)
  ExcelSvc -> Sheet: getRow(r)
  Sheet --> ExcelSvc: Row
  ExcelSvc -> Row: getCell(0) → 工号
  note right of ExcelSvc #F0F8FF
    **解析行数据:**
    A列=工号, B列=考勤扣款值
    → map.put(工号, {itemId: value})
  end note
end
ExcelSvc --> Ctrl: Map<String, Map<Long, Double>>\n{ "EMP001": {1:-200, 2:3000} }
Ctrl --> Client: ApiResponse(导入数据)
@enduml
